<figureCitation box="[1045,1160,237,258]" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="5.[144,223,1853,1872]" captionTargetBox="[367,1199,983,1822]" captionTargetId="figure-346@5.[367,1199,983,1823]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Figure 3. Tergites of investigated species, lateral view. A, Chrysotoxum festivum A; B, Chrysotoxum festivum B; C, Chrysotoxum elegans; D, Chrysotoxum elegans – intermediate form; E, Chrysotoxum octomaculatum." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4720364" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4720364/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="97">Fig. 3C–D</figureCitation>
